{"tid":860334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人細過連宣傳易都會睇?","createTime":"2018-10-13T09:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T16:26:16.000Z","uid":49147,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"25924fea8e3a8e943c481bf6a36d2f23609da9b3","tid":860334,"uid":49147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"得成女傭融入家中..<br />\n認住金寶鐘...<br />\n屌用愛膚堅啦...<br />\n美源髮彩 無得彈...<br />\n時興隆 美食盡在不言中...<br />\n仲有一系列煩膠旺旺廣告<br />\n<br />\n幾廿年無睇電視,突然諗起細過係電視睇咩龍珠或者深夜卡通中間永遠有宣傳易同咩碧桂園廣告,我又真係會好認真咁睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細過真係好易滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dafcc513a75429c2f899b99e2b047c2021f81e","tid":860334,"uid":200641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"唔撚洗用劍嘅"},{"pid":"30a513bde57b7d696ea0a781414abd3364b1a7d8","tid":860334,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:13:41.000Z","msg":"力之霸音響 超乎你想像"},{"pid":"7b47087a08b1f34527c5b8bb3d6e3ae708e4eb73","tid":860334,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"能者~ Expertttttttt"},{"pid":"46f8520fc8c5aeb217701dc1ef4945227d4c4f94","tid":860334,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"鐵將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜鳩無線門鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前d大陸廣告淨係會匿係宣傳易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b246d54aa5f396fe459fb50eefcd7b59671765cb","tid":860334,"uid":182930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"我可以幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9a9d2e6bfe48a1b58b9ea868a66088b30d70a9","tid":860334,"uid